{
  "stem": "747.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't-- we-- we had-- you know, we were quite secure at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the first bomb fell on Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was a provocated-- was provoked by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They killed the-- our president's son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was really a provocation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they blamed it on the Americans, and they started the war with-- with America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the first bomb fell out in Budapest, my husband was injured.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was working in a labor battalion, demolishing old houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was buried alive there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Luckily, he made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But a lot of people were killed then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after then, it was down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Sliding down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Every day, harder and harder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "New laws that you're not supposed to do this, you can do this, food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then we started to get a the ticket, a ration ticket for food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans took everything out from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So the people, in general, suffered-- was a loss of-- with-- life started to be hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And was a great inflation, and the stores stayed open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Opened, but was empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so when it came 1944, it was a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nervous city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Very-- everybody was on-- you know, it just felt that something is coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Something unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
